[
  {
    "startTime": 13.228,
    "endTime": 17.262,
    "text": "In many patriarchal societies and tribal societies,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.262,
    "endTime": 22.487000000000002,
    "text": "fathers are usually known by their sons,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.487,
    "endTime": 25.703,
    "text": "but I'm one of the few fathers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.703,
    "endTime": 27.747,
    "text": "who is known by his daughter,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.747,
    "endTime": 29.373,
    "text": "and I am proud of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.373,
    "endTime": 35.81,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.81,
    "endTime": 38.658,
    "text": "Malala started her campaign for education"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.658,
    "endTime": 41.545,
    "text": "and stood for her rights in 2007,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.545,
    "endTime": 46.103,
    "text": "and when her efforts were honored in 2011,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.103,
    "endTime": 49.543,
    "text": "and she was given the national youth peace prize,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.543,
    "endTime": 51.412,
    "text": "and she became a very famous,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.412,
    "endTime": 55.455999999999996,
    "text": "very popular young girl of her country."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.456,
    "endTime": 58.784000000000006,
    "text": "Before that, she was my daughter,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.784,
    "endTime": 62.741,
    "text": "but now I am her father."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.741,
    "endTime": 64.496,
    "text": "Ladies and gentlemen,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.496,
    "endTime": 67.643,
    "text": "if we glance to human history,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.643,
    "endTime": 70.471,
    "text": "the story of women"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.471,
    "endTime": 73.84700000000001,
    "text": "is the story of injustice,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.847,
    "endTime": 75.907,
    "text": "inequality,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.907,
    "endTime": 81.21799999999999,
    "text": "violence and exploitation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.218,
    "endTime": 83.053,
    "text": "You see,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.053,
    "endTime": 87.204,
    "text": "in patriarchal societies,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.204,
    "endTime": 89.64599999999999,
    "text": "right from the very beginning,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.646,
    "endTime": 92.652,
    "text": "when a girl is born,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.652,
    "endTime": 96.932,
    "text": "her birth is not celebrated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.932,
    "endTime": 99.096,
    "text": "She is not welcomed,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.096,
    "endTime": 101.872,
    "text": "neither by father nor by mother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.872,
    "endTime": 103.557,
    "text": "The neighborhood comes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.557,
    "endTime": 106.058,
    "text": "and commiserates with the mother,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.058,
    "endTime": 111.152,
    "text": "and nobody congratulates the father."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.152,
    "endTime": 115.467,
    "text": "And a mother is very uncomfortable"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.467,
    "endTime": 119.834,
    "text": "for having a girl child."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.834,
    "endTime": 123.09400000000001,
    "text": "When she gives birth to the first girl child,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.094,
    "endTime": 127.18299999999999,
    "text": "first daughter, she is sad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.183,
    "endTime": 130.93,
    "text": "When she gives birth to the second daughter,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.93,
    "endTime": 132.77700000000002,
    "text": "she is shocked,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.777,
    "endTime": 136.16099999999997,
    "text": "and in the expectation of a son,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.161,
    "endTime": 139.367,
    "text": "when she gives birth to a third daughter,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.367,
    "endTime": 144.90599999999998,
    "text": "she feels guilty like a criminal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.906,
    "endTime": 147.54,
    "text": "Not only the mother suffers,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.54,
    "endTime": 150.277,
    "text": "but the daughter, the newly born daughter,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.277,
    "endTime": 152.41199999999998,
    "text": "when she grows old,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.412,
    "endTime": 154.547,
    "text": "she suffers too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.547,
    "endTime": 156.6,
    "text": "At the age of five,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.6,
    "endTime": 159.929,
    "text": "while she should be going to school,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.929,
    "endTime": 161.672,
    "text": "she stays at home"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.672,
    "endTime": 166.29399999999998,
    "text": "and her brothers are admitted in a school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.294,
    "endTime": 168.887,
    "text": "Until the age of 12, somehow,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.887,
    "endTime": 171.528,
    "text": "she has a good life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.528,
    "endTime": 173.19899999999998,
    "text": "She can have fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.199,
    "endTime": 176.388,
    "text": "She can play with her friends in the streets,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.388,
    "endTime": 178.427,
    "text": "and she can move around in the streets"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.427,
    "endTime": 181.202,
    "text": "like a butterfly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.202,
    "endTime": 185.017,
    "text": "But when she enters her teens,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.017,
    "endTime": 187.357,
    "text": "when she becomes 13 years old,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.357,
    "endTime": 190.976,
    "text": "she is forbidden to go out of her home"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.976,
    "endTime": 194.468,
    "text": "without a male escort."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.468,
    "endTime": 199.843,
    "text": "She is confined under the four walls of her home."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.843,
    "endTime": 205.03699999999998,
    "text": "She is no more a free individual."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.037,
    "endTime": 208.05700000000002,
    "text": "She becomes the so-called honor"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.057,
    "endTime": 210.53799999999998,
    "text": "of her father and of her brothers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.538,
    "endTime": 213.988,
    "text": "and of her family,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.988,
    "endTime": 216.676,
    "text": "and if she transgresses"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.676,
    "endTime": 219.887,
    "text": "the code of that so-called honor,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.887,
    "endTime": 224.251,
    "text": "she could even be killed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.251,
    "endTime": 228.252,
    "text": "And it is also interesting that this so-called"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.252,
    "endTime": 229.615,
    "text": "code of honor,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.615,
    "endTime": 233.305,
    "text": "it does not only affect the life of a girl,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.305,
    "endTime": 235.431,
    "text": "it also affects the life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.431,
    "endTime": 240.23000000000002,
    "text": "of the male members of the family."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.23,
    "endTime": 246.82299999999998,
    "text": "I know a family of seven sisters and one brother,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.823,
    "endTime": 248.645,
    "text": "and that one brother,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.645,
    "endTime": 252.149,
    "text": "he has migrated to the Gulf countries,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.149,
    "endTime": 254.844,
    "text": "to earn a living for his seven sisters"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.844,
    "endTime": 257.192,
    "text": "and parents,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.192,
    "endTime": 263.046,
    "text": "because he thinks that it will be humiliating"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.046,
    "endTime": 265.768,
    "text": "if his seven sisters learn a skill"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.768,
    "endTime": 268.14799999999997,
    "text": "and they go out of the home"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.148,
    "endTime": 272.29900000000004,
    "text": "and earn some livelihood."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.299,
    "endTime": 273.88899999999995,
    "text": "So this brother,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.889,
    "endTime": 277.242,
    "text": "he sacrifices the joys of his life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.242,
    "endTime": 280.634,
    "text": "and the happiness of his sisters"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.634,
    "endTime": 285.218,
    "text": "at the altar of so-called honor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.218,
    "endTime": 286.752,
    "text": "And there is one more norm"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.752,
    "endTime": 289.11,
    "text": "of the patriarchal societies"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.11,
    "endTime": 293.56,
    "text": "that is called obedience."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.56,
    "endTime": 297.346,
    "text": "A good girl is supposed to be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.346,
    "endTime": 302.594,
    "text": "very quiet, very humble"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.594,
    "endTime": 306.565,
    "text": "and very submissive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.565,
    "endTime": 307.904,
    "text": "It is the criteria."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.904,
    "endTime": 311.736,
    "text": "The role model good girl should be very quiet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.736,
    "endTime": 314.025,
    "text": "She is supposed to be silent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.025,
    "endTime": 317.19599999999997,
    "text": "and she is supposed to accept the decisions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.196,
    "endTime": 319.41600000000005,
    "text": "of her father and mother"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.416,
    "endTime": 322.641,
    "text": "and the decisions of elders,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.641,
    "endTime": 325.047,
    "text": "even if she does not like them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.047,
    "endTime": 328.37600000000003,
    "text": "If she is married to a man she doesn't like"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.376,
    "endTime": 331.118,
    "text": "or if she is married to an old man,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.118,
    "endTime": 332.678,
    "text": "she has to accept,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.678,
    "endTime": 335.19599999999997,
    "text": "because she does not want to be dubbed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 335.196,
    "endTime": 337.819,
    "text": "as disobedient."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.819,
    "endTime": 339.451,
    "text": "If she is married very early,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.451,
    "endTime": 340.925,
    "text": "she has to accept."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.925,
    "endTime": 344.947,
    "text": "Otherwise, she will be called disobedient."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.947,
    "endTime": 347.75,
    "text": "And what happens at the end?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.75,
    "endTime": 349.505,
    "text": "In the words of a poetess,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.505,
    "endTime": 352.292,
    "text": "she is wedded, bedded,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.292,
    "endTime": 357.46299999999997,
    "text": "and then she gives birth to more sons and daughters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.463,
    "endTime": 360.232,
    "text": "And it is the irony of the situation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.232,
    "endTime": 362.564,
    "text": "that this mother,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.564,
    "endTime": 365.61600000000004,
    "text": "she teaches the same lesson of obedience"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 365.616,
    "endTime": 366.676,
    "text": "to her daughter"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.676,
    "endTime": 371.109,
    "text": "and the same lesson of honor to her sons."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.109,
    "endTime": 377.99699999999996,
    "text": "And this vicious cycle goes on, goes on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.997,
    "endTime": 380.524,
    "text": "Ladies and gentlemen,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.524,
    "endTime": 383.746,
    "text": "this plight of millions of women"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.746,
    "endTime": 386.578,
    "text": "could be changed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 386.578,
    "endTime": 388.953,
    "text": "if we think differently,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 388.953,
    "endTime": 392.93399999999997,
    "text": "if women and men think differently,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.934,
    "endTime": 397.15200000000004,
    "text": "if men and women in the tribal and patriarchal societies"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397.152,
    "endTime": 399.135,
    "text": "in the developing countries,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 399.135,
    "endTime": 402.046,
    "text": "if they can break a few norms"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.046,
    "endTime": 406.65,
    "text": "of family and society,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 406.65,
    "endTime": 412.13,
    "text": "if they can abolish the discriminatory laws"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 412.13,
    "endTime": 414.658,
    "text": "of the systems in their states,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 414.658,
    "endTime": 416.949,
    "text": "which go against the basic human rights"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 416.949,
    "endTime": 420.743,
    "text": "of the women."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 420.743,
    "endTime": 425.98699999999997,
    "text": "Dear brothers and sisters, when Malala was born,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 425.987,
    "endTime": 428.14000000000004,
    "text": "and for the first time,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428.14,
    "endTime": 429.414,
    "text": "believe me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 429.414,
    "endTime": 434.39099999999996,
    "text": "I don't like newborn children, to be honest,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 434.391,
    "endTime": 438.173,
    "text": "but when I went and I looked into her eyes,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 438.173,
    "endTime": 440.293,
    "text": "believe me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.293,
    "endTime": 444.274,
    "text": "I got extremely honored."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444.274,
    "endTime": 446.444,
    "text": "And long before she was born,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 446.444,
    "endTime": 449.48,
    "text": "I thought about her name,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 449.48,
    "endTime": 452.76500000000004,
    "text": "and I was fascinated with a heroic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 452.765,
    "endTime": 456.63,
    "text": "legendary freedom fighter in Afghanistan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 456.63,
    "endTime": 461.639,
    "text": "Her name was Malalai of Maiwand,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 461.639,
    "endTime": 465.92400000000004,
    "text": "and I named my daughter after her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 465.924,
    "endTime": 468.916,
    "text": "A few days after Malala was born,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 468.916,
    "endTime": 470.655,
    "text": "my daughter was born,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 470.655,
    "endTime": 472.313,
    "text": "my cousin came --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 472.313,
    "endTime": 474.281,
    "text": "and it was a coincidence --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 474.281,
    "endTime": 476.996,
    "text": "he came to my home"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 476.996,
    "endTime": 479.70099999999996,
    "text": "and he brought a family tree,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 479.701,
    "endTime": 483.369,
    "text": "a family tree of the Yousafzai family,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 483.369,
    "endTime": 485.925,
    "text": "and when I looked at the family tree,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 485.925,
    "endTime": 491.978,
    "text": "it traced back to 300 years of our ancestors."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 491.978,
    "endTime": 496.375,
    "text": "But when I looked, all were men,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 496.375,
    "endTime": 498.797,
    "text": "and I picked my pen,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 498.797,
    "endTime": 500.80100000000004,
    "text": "drew a line from my name,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 500.801,
    "endTime": 505.585,
    "text": "and wrote, \"Malala.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505.585,
    "endTime": 508.35499999999996,
    "text": "And when she grow old,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 508.355,
    "endTime": 511.93800000000005,
    "text": "when she was four and a half years old,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 511.938,
    "endTime": 515.4739999999999,
    "text": "I admitted her in my school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 515.474,
    "endTime": 518.38,
    "text": "You will be asking, then, why should I mention about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.38,
    "endTime": 520.882,
    "text": "the admission of a girl in a school?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 520.882,
    "endTime": 522.9369999999999,
    "text": "Yes, I must mention it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 522.937,
    "endTime": 526.022,
    "text": "It may be taken for granted in Canada,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 526.022,
    "endTime": 529.849,
    "text": "in America, in many developed countries,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 529.849,
    "endTime": 532.307,
    "text": "but in poor countries,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.307,
    "endTime": 535.875,
    "text": "in patriarchal societies, in tribal societies,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.875,
    "endTime": 539.489,
    "text": "it's a big event for the life of girl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 539.489,
    "endTime": 543.128,
    "text": "Enrollment in a school means"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 543.128,
    "endTime": 548.8770000000001,
    "text": "recognition of her identity and her name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 548.877,
    "endTime": 550.555,
    "text": "Admission in a school means"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 550.555,
    "endTime": 554.237,
    "text": "that she has entered the world of dreams"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.237,
    "endTime": 555.9,
    "text": "and aspirations"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 555.9,
    "endTime": 559.4119999999999,
    "text": "where she can explore her potentials"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 559.412,
    "endTime": 562.658,
    "text": "for her future life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 562.658,
    "endTime": 564.737,
    "text": "I have five sisters,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 564.737,
    "endTime": 568.0509999999999,
    "text": "and none of them could go to school,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 568.051,
    "endTime": 569.625,
    "text": "and you will be astonished,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.625,
    "endTime": 573.735,
    "text": "two weeks before,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 573.735,
    "endTime": 578.018,
    "text": "when I was filling out the Canadian visa form,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 578.018,
    "endTime": 582.683,
    "text": "and I was filling out the family part of the form,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.683,
    "endTime": 584.7669999999999,
    "text": "I could not recall"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 584.767,
    "endTime": 588.772,
    "text": "the surnames of some of my sisters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 588.772,
    "endTime": 590.6210000000001,
    "text": "And the reason was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 590.621,
    "endTime": 593.913,
    "text": "that I have never, never seen the names"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 593.913,
    "endTime": 599.739,
    "text": "of my sisters written on any document."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.739,
    "endTime": 602.6790000000001,
    "text": "That was the reason that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 602.679,
    "endTime": 606.212,
    "text": "I valued my daughter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.212,
    "endTime": 610.525,
    "text": "What my father could not give to my sisters"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 610.525,
    "endTime": 612.28,
    "text": "and to his daughters,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 612.28,
    "endTime": 616.521,
    "text": "I thought I must change it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 616.521,
    "endTime": 619.5279999999999,
    "text": "I used to appreciate the intelligence"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 619.528,
    "endTime": 623.2,
    "text": "and the brilliance of my daughter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 623.2,
    "endTime": 625.7940000000001,
    "text": "I encouraged her to sit with me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 625.794,
    "endTime": 627.453,
    "text": "when my friends used to come."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 627.453,
    "endTime": 632.237,
    "text": "I encouraged her to go with me to different meetings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 632.237,
    "endTime": 633.8979999999999,
    "text": "And all these good values,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 633.898,
    "endTime": 637.1080000000001,
    "text": "I tried to inculcate in her personality."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 637.108,
    "endTime": 640.771,
    "text": "And this was not only she, only Malala."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 640.771,
    "endTime": 643.507,
    "text": "I imparted all these good values"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 643.507,
    "endTime": 648.05,
    "text": "to my school, girl students and boy students as well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 648.05,
    "endTime": 652.429,
    "text": "I used education for emancipation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 652.429,
    "endTime": 654.294,
    "text": "I taught my girls,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 654.294,
    "endTime": 656.249,
    "text": "I taught my girl students,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 656.249,
    "endTime": 661.318,
    "text": "to unlearn the lesson of obedience."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 661.318,
    "endTime": 664.283,
    "text": "I taught my boy students"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.283,
    "endTime": 673.696,
    "text": "to unlearn the lesson of so-called pseudo-honor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673.696,
    "endTime": 677.681,
    "text": "Dear brothers and sisters,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 677.681,
    "endTime": 682.264,
    "text": "we were striving for more rights for women,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 682.264,
    "endTime": 685.886,
    "text": "and we were struggling to have more,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.886,
    "endTime": 690.1129999999999,
    "text": "more and more space for the women in society."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 690.113,
    "endTime": 693.326,
    "text": "But we came across a new phenomenon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 693.326,
    "endTime": 695.8190000000001,
    "text": "It was lethal to human rights"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 695.819,
    "endTime": 699.2669999999999,
    "text": "and particularly to women's rights."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 699.267,
    "endTime": 703.9440000000001,
    "text": "It was called Talibanization."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.944,
    "endTime": 707.632,
    "text": "It means a complete negation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 707.632,
    "endTime": 709.842,
    "text": "of women's participation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 709.842,
    "endTime": 716.037,
    "text": "in all political, economical and social activities."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 716.037,
    "endTime": 719.5840000000001,
    "text": "Hundreds of schools were lost."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 719.584,
    "endTime": 725.8149999999999,
    "text": "Girls were prohibited from going to school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 725.815,
    "endTime": 729.5210000000001,
    "text": "Women were forced to wear veils"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 729.521,
    "endTime": 733.077,
    "text": "and they were stopped from going to the markets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 733.077,
    "endTime": 735.661,
    "text": "Musicians were silenced,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 735.661,
    "endTime": 737.6179999999999,
    "text": "girls were flogged"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 737.618,
    "endTime": 741.101,
    "text": "and singers were killed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 741.101,
    "endTime": 742.975,
    "text": "Millions were suffering,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 742.975,
    "endTime": 746.22,
    "text": "but few spoke,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 746.22,
    "endTime": 748.4440000000001,
    "text": "and it was the most scary thing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 748.444,
    "endTime": 754.53,
    "text": "when you have all around such people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 754.53,
    "endTime": 756.5559999999999,
    "text": "who kill and who flog,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 756.556,
    "endTime": 757.8520000000001,
    "text": "and you speak for your rights."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 757.852,
    "endTime": 762.059,
    "text": "It's really the most scary thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 762.059,
    "endTime": 763.952,
    "text": "At the age of 10,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 763.952,
    "endTime": 768.196,
    "text": "Malala stood, and she stood for the right"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 768.196,
    "endTime": 770.5070000000001,
    "text": "of education."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 770.507,
    "endTime": 775.279,
    "text": "She wrote a diary for the BBC blog,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 775.279,
    "endTime": 777.483,
    "text": "she volunteered herself"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 777.483,
    "endTime": 781.077,
    "text": "for the New York Times documentaries,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 781.077,
    "endTime": 785.993,
    "text": "and she spoke from every platform she could."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 785.993,
    "endTime": 790.3810000000001,
    "text": "And her voice was the most powerful voice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 790.381,
    "endTime": 796.634,
    "text": "It spread like a crescendo all around the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 796.634,
    "endTime": 798.486,
    "text": "And that was the reason the Taliban"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 798.486,
    "endTime": 802.817,
    "text": "could not tolerate her campaign,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 802.817,
    "endTime": 805.666,
    "text": "and on October 9 2012,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 805.666,
    "endTime": 811.4150000000001,
    "text": "she was shot in the head at point blank range."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 811.415,
    "endTime": 815.56,
    "text": "It was a doomsday for my family and for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 815.56,
    "endTime": 821.3789999999999,
    "text": "The world turned into a big black hole."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 821.379,
    "endTime": 823.0450000000001,
    "text": "While my daughter was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 823.045,
    "endTime": 826.497,
    "text": "on the verge of life and death,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 826.497,
    "endTime": 830.336,
    "text": "I whispered into the ears of my wife,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 830.336,
    "endTime": 833.438,
    "text": "\"Should I be blamed for what happened"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 833.438,
    "endTime": 837.114,
    "text": "to my daughter and your daughter?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 837.114,
    "endTime": 839.635,
    "text": "And she abruptly told me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 839.635,
    "endTime": 842.146,
    "text": "\"Please don't blame yourself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 842.146,
    "endTime": 845.362,
    "text": "You stood for the right cause."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 845.362,
    "endTime": 847.497,
    "text": "You put your life at stake"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 847.497,
    "endTime": 848.9,
    "text": "for the cause of truth,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 848.9,
    "endTime": 850.081,
    "text": "for the cause of peace,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 850.081,
    "endTime": 852.189,
    "text": "and for the cause of education,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 852.189,
    "endTime": 854.2379999999999,
    "text": "and your daughter in inspired from you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 854.238,
    "endTime": 856.469,
    "text": "and she joined you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 856.469,
    "endTime": 858.144,
    "text": "You both were on the right path"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 858.144,
    "endTime": 861.517,
    "text": "and God will protect her.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 861.517,
    "endTime": 864.863,
    "text": "These few words meant a lot to me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 864.863,
    "endTime": 868.974,
    "text": "and I didn't ask this question again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 868.974,
    "endTime": 873.094,
    "text": "When Malala was in the hospital,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 873.094,
    "endTime": 876.341,
    "text": "and she was going through the severe pains"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 876.341,
    "endTime": 878.861,
    "text": "and she had had severe headaches"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 878.861,
    "endTime": 882.049,
    "text": "because her facial nerve was cut down,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 882.049,
    "endTime": 884.501,
    "text": "I used to see a dark shadow"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 884.501,
    "endTime": 890.038,
    "text": "spreading on the face of my wife."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 890.038,
    "endTime": 896.139,
    "text": "But my daughter never complained."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 896.139,
    "endTime": 898.2,
    "text": "She used to tell us,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 898.2,
    "endTime": 900.2510000000001,
    "text": "\"I'm fine with my crooked smile"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 900.251,
    "endTime": 902.9929999999999,
    "text": "and with my numbness in my face."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 902.993,
    "endTime": 905.072,
    "text": "I'll be okay. Please don't worry.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 905.072,
    "endTime": 907.201,
    "text": "She was a solace for us,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 907.201,
    "endTime": 912.12,
    "text": "and she consoled us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 912.12,
    "endTime": 916.341,
    "text": "Dear brothers and sisters,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 916.341,
    "endTime": 918.963,
    "text": "we learned from her how to be resilient"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 918.963,
    "endTime": 922.2679999999999,
    "text": "in the most difficult times,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 922.268,
    "endTime": 925.2760000000001,
    "text": "and I'm glad to share with you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 925.276,
    "endTime": 931.168,
    "text": "that despite being an icon"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 931.168,
    "endTime": 933.997,
    "text": "for the rights of children and women,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 933.997,
    "endTime": 939.29,
    "text": "she is like any 16-year old girl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 939.29,
    "endTime": 944.4219999999999,
    "text": "She cries when her homework is incomplete."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 944.422,
    "endTime": 946.49,
    "text": "She quarrels with her brothers,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 946.49,
    "endTime": 950.213,
    "text": "and I am very happy for that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 950.213,
    "endTime": 952.616,
    "text": "People ask me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 952.616,
    "endTime": 956.108,
    "text": "what special is in my mentorship"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 956.108,
    "endTime": 958.6479999999999,
    "text": "which has made Malala so bold"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 958.648,
    "endTime": 963.14,
    "text": "and so courageous and so vocal and poised?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 963.14,
    "endTime": 969.415,
    "text": "I tell them, don't ask me what I did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 969.415,
    "endTime": 973.276,
    "text": "Ask me what I did not do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 973.276,
    "endTime": 978.5329999999999,
    "text": "I did not clip her wings, and that's all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 978.533,
    "endTime": 981.415,
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 981.415,
    "endTime": 986.911,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 986.911,
    "endTime": 996.911,
    "text": "Thank you. Thank you very much. Thank you. (Applause)"
  }
]